Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStarSearch
    The class that is used to hold the data structures and behaviours to carry out the A Star (A*) search algorithm on the puzzle to be solved, using the heuristic choice made by the user the command line arguments.
    BreadthFirstSearch
    The class that is used to hold the data structures and behaviours to carry out the depth first search algorithm on the puzzle to be solved.
    DepthFirstSearch
    The class that is used to hold the data structures and behaviours to carry out the depth first search algorithm on the puzzle to be solved.
    FileIO
    The class that handles all the loading in of files from the file system.
    GridState
    The class to represent a single state of the puzzle at any one time.
    Path
    Class to collect the gridState objects that are on the path the algorithms take to solve the 8-puzzle.
    Solve
    The main class of the program, containing the main method, so that the program can be run from the command line.
